  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201503/205deabd53294f1a805894b4b4514083.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px; height: 300px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.yun.hjfile.cn/entry/201501/ceca10ab-76bc-432a-83da-344492e86912.jpg!topic\" style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\" /><strong style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">新词</strong></p>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><a href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/decacorn\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(16, 113, 181);\" target=\"_blank\">decacorn</a></strong></span></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n\t\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">n</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">. A technology company that is less than ten years old and worth more than ten billion dollars.</span><span style=\"color: #008000;\"><span>&ldquo;十角兽&rdquo;就是指这种创业不到10年但市值超过百亿美元的科技公司。</span></span></div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">今天新词速递送给大家的就是</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(0, 102, 0);\"><strong>decacorn</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">这个词，我把它译为&ldquo;十角兽&rdquo;公司。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.yun.hjfile.cn/entry/201501/ceca10ab-76bc-432a-83da-344492e86912.jpg!topic\" /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>编者按</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\tBillion-dollar companies join a club of &quot;unicorns&quot;, a term used to explain how rare they are. But there are more than 50 of them now. There's a new buzzword, &quot;decacorn&quot;, for those over $10 billion, which includes Airbnb, Dropbox, Pinterest, Snapchat, and Uber.之前，&ldquo;独角兽&rdquo;这个词用来指市值超过10亿美元的公司，因为这样的公司太稀少了。但是，现在&ldquo;独角兽&rdquo;公司的数量已经超过50个了。于是&ldquo;十角兽&rdquo;应运而生，用来指市值超过百亿美元的公司，比如Airbnb、Dropbox、Pinterest、Snapchat和Uber等。</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">该词仿照了英文单词unicorn（独角兽</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">），</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">由deca-（十）+corn构成。其实，独角兽是神话中的一种虚构的动物，</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">与马差不多大，头顶有一犄角，长约一英尺半，因其神秘不常见而闻名。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i3.s.yun.hjfile.cn/entry/201501/ceca10ab-76bc-432a-83da-344492e86912.jpg!topic\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">八卦一下</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">最初，对于技术领域新企业的价值估计据说有这样一种衡量标准：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;独角兽&rdquo;式的企业</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">（<a href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Unicorn\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(16, 113, 181);\" target=\"_blank\">Unicorn</a>）= $1B</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;十角兽&rdquo;式的企业</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Decacorn</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">= $10B</span><br />\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&ldquo;百角兽&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">式的企业</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">（Centicorn）= $100B</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">八卦结束，我们可以从中学到三个前缀：uni-\\deci-\\centi-。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(229, 102, 0);\"><strong>uni-</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">表示&ldquo;一&rdquo;、&ldquo;单&rdquo;、&ldquo;一方&rdquo;之义，如：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">unilateral（单边的），uniform（统一）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(76, 51, 229);\"><strong>deci-</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">表示&quot;十分之一&quot;，如：decimeter(</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">分米</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">)、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">decimal（小数</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(204, 51, 229);\"><strong>centi-</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">表示&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">一百&rdquo;，如：</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/centipede\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(16, 113, 181);\" target=\"_blank\">centipede</a>（</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">百足之虫</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">蜈蚣</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">centigram（厘克</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">\n\t\t<strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 15.555556297302246px;\"><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/abcenglish/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">欢迎来到》》》零基础英语从头学，这里你可以找到学习英语的勇气和魔法书&hellip;&hellip;</a></strong></p>\n\t<p style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 15.555556297302246px; line-height: 28px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">\n\t\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><strong>还有</strong></span><a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/cihui/\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 90, 148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;&gt;&gt;沪江词汇社，等着你哦！</a></p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725448/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p725448\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725268/\">裙子长短决定个性：婊砸或圣母</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p718540/\">汪涵救场获赞: 英国人也会优雅的骂人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725409/\">如果你的数学老师长这样 还能专心听课吗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725255/\">国外知乎：如何成为世界首富？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725304/\">助记法才是背词王道: 从生活想到单词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p708340/\">新科技 Wifi信号能治病</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725287/\">蒙古发现200年前和尚木乃伊 仍成打坐姿态</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725256/\">Quora精选 如何用英语吐槽经济学家</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725405/\">老美五大禁忌话题  你中枪了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p725150/\">神奇:一个能助你找到真爱的数学公式！</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\